title: Police arrest 3 Cleveland teens for having loaded guns
text:
Police arrest 3 Cleveland teens for having loaded guns 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
Three teenage boys, ages 15 and 16, were arrested on Cleveland's near East Side Thursday night for concealing loaded weapons, police say....
